1
00:01:36,350 --> 00:01:39,000
[A Love Never Lost]

2
00:01:40,610 --> 00:01:41,900
[Episode 7]

3
00:01:55,700 --> 00:01:56,340
This is it.

4
00:01:56,560 --> 00:01:57,289
Liang Xiang.

5
00:01:57,479 --> 00:01:58,310
You go first.

6
00:01:58,789 --> 00:01:59,990
Why should I go first?

7
00:02:01,790 --> 00:02:02,430
Look.

8
00:02:02,820 --> 00:02:04,510
The important guests are here.

9
00:02:04,510 --> 00:02:06,280
They are here for you, Tufang.

10
00:02:06,840 --> 00:02:07,840
For me?

11
00:02:08,520 --> 00:02:09,590
Why me?

12
00:02:10,350 --> 00:02:12,080
They are from your main family.

13
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:13,580
Don't you recognize them?

14
00:02:13,590 --> 00:02:15,380
The one leading them is Prince Qing's son.

15
00:02:15,380 --> 00:02:16,590
Young Prince Zaizheng.

16
00:02:16,590 --> 00:02:18,590
The one behind is the Japanese envoy.

17
00:02:18,590 --> 00:02:19,920
Young Prince Zaizheng?

18
00:02:20,360 --> 00:02:21,360
I don't know him.

19
00:02:21,810 --> 00:02:22,710
Aren't you here in place

20
00:02:22,710 --> 00:02:24,840
of someone from Prince Qing's family?

21
00:02:25,230 --> 00:02:26,490
You've never seen him?

22
00:02:26,829 --> 00:02:27,829
I don't know him.

23
00:02:28,360 --> 00:02:29,900
Your ancestor was Prince Rui.

24
00:02:29,900 --> 00:02:31,360
His father is Prince Qing.

25
00:02:31,390 --> 00:02:32,150
You took his place

26
00:02:32,150 --> 00:02:33,079
to study abroad.

27
00:02:33,240 --> 00:02:34,240
It doesn't matter if you don't know him.

28
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,260
You'll know him once you go in there.

29
00:02:35,260 --> 00:02:36,520
Why should I meet him?

30
00:02:36,640 --> 00:02:37,570
Is it necessary?

31
00:02:38,000 --> 00:02:38,590
I'm not going.

32
00:02:38,590 --> 00:02:39,790
You can go if you want.

33
00:02:41,710 --> 00:02:43,240
I already told him you were coming.

34
00:02:43,240 --> 00:02:45,000
If you don't show up now,

35
00:02:45,630 --> 00:02:46,710
what do I tell him?

36
00:02:46,840 --> 00:02:48,370
Did I ask you to contact him?

37
00:02:48,430 --> 00:02:49,960
You got yourself into this,

38
00:02:50,000 --> 00:02:51,260
sort it out on your own.

39
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:54,150
Are you going to a restaurant with me,

40
00:02:54,150 --> 00:02:55,610
or will you stick with him?

41
00:02:57,910 --> 00:02:59,310
Look at what you've done.

42
00:03:01,070 --> 00:03:02,600
Even if both of you don't go,

43
00:03:02,710 --> 00:03:04,510
I have to go in and settle things.

44
00:03:04,590 --> 00:03:05,240
Okay.

45
00:03:05,400 --> 00:03:06,680
The two of you can go and socialize.

46
00:03:06,680 --> 00:03:07,960
I'm going to eat alone.

47
00:03:11,280 --> 00:03:11,910
Tufang!

48
00:03:12,400 --> 00:03:13,120
My goodness.

49
00:03:13,120 --> 00:03:14,720
Why are you so bad-tempered?

50
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:17,079
Fine.

51
00:03:18,120 --> 00:03:18,800
I, Li Renjun,

52
00:03:18,800 --> 00:03:19,980
will sacrifice myself to appease the lord.

53
00:03:19,980 --> 00:03:20,680
Go in by yourself.

54
00:03:20,680 --> 00:03:22,810
I'll accompany him to the restaurant.

55
00:03:24,079 --> 00:03:24,730
Tufang!

56
00:03:31,430 --> 00:03:32,490
Qianli, my friend.

57
00:03:34,120 --> 00:03:35,120
Don't you think Kaizhi

58
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,360
is such a strange guy?

59
00:03:37,590 --> 00:03:39,560
He's just a military student.

60
00:03:39,560 --> 00:03:40,960
But instead of studying,

61
00:03:41,079 --> 00:03:42,870
he insists on getting involved

62
00:03:42,870 --> 00:03:44,000
with the officials visiting Japan.

63
00:03:44,000 --> 00:03:45,870
He's even dragging me along with him.

64
00:03:45,870 --> 00:03:47,120
What does he want?

65
00:03:51,960 --> 00:03:53,120
Enjoy.

66
00:03:55,680 --> 00:03:57,000
Thank you.

67
00:03:58,800 --> 00:03:59,800
His spoken Japanese

68
00:03:59,800 --> 00:04:00,870
is awful.

69
00:04:01,590 --> 00:04:03,710
But he insists on being the tour guide,

70
00:04:03,710 --> 00:04:04,590
But he's eager to follow

71
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:06,190
anyone and everyone around.

72
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:06,960
Tell me.

73
00:04:07,520 --> 00:04:08,680
What does he want?

74
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:12,240
We call that

75
00:04:13,760 --> 00:04:16,000
walking the tightrope with a blindfold.

76
00:04:16,000 --> 00:04:17,399
Too bold for his own good.

77
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,800
Among us military students in Japan,

78
00:04:20,800 --> 00:04:23,040
Yang Kaizhi is the most daring.

79
00:04:23,530 --> 00:04:24,600
He's not afraid of anyone

80
00:04:24,600 --> 00:04:26,260
and interacts with everyone.

81
00:04:26,270 --> 00:04:27,870
Who else did he hang out with?

82
00:04:31,240 --> 00:04:32,070
Last month,

83
00:04:32,360 --> 00:04:33,360
in Kanda.

84
00:04:33,680 --> 00:04:35,120
Guess who he met.

85
00:04:38,000 --> 00:04:38,480
Who?

86
00:04:38,600 --> 00:04:40,360
A whole bunch of rebels.

87
00:04:41,670 --> 00:04:42,400
Really?

88
00:04:43,000 --> 00:04:43,920
That day,

89
00:04:44,510 --> 00:04:46,350
he dragged me to see Liang Qichao.

90
00:04:46,350 --> 00:04:47,409
From Kang's party!

91
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,370
Can I meet Liang Qichao?

92
00:04:49,750 --> 00:04:51,159
Absolutely not!

93
00:04:51,390 --> 00:04:53,050
I was recommended by Mr. Yuan.

94
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,610
Mr. Yuan is rivals with Kang and Liang.

95
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,040
If he keeps this up,

96
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:58,920
sooner or later, his name will show up

97
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,450
on the court's wanted list.

98
00:05:00,830 --> 00:05:02,330
His name was on that list

99
00:05:02,360 --> 00:05:04,070
ever since he left Shanghai.

100
00:05:05,390 --> 00:05:06,070
Really?

101
00:05:07,190 --> 00:05:07,750
However,

102
00:05:08,190 --> 00:05:09,520
the imperial officials

103
00:05:09,600 --> 00:05:11,000
can't do anything to him.

104
00:05:11,240 --> 00:05:11,920
Somehow,

105
00:05:12,000 --> 00:05:14,600
he hooked up with the Viceroy of Liangjiang.

106
00:05:14,830 --> 00:05:17,160
Liu Kunyi personally recommended him for this program.

107
00:05:17,160 --> 00:05:17,870
Besides,

108
00:05:18,120 --> 00:05:19,990
for some reason, Mr. Song of the

109
00:05:20,120 --> 00:05:21,240
Shanghai Business Association

110
00:05:21,240 --> 00:05:23,100
is also secretly supporting him.

111
00:05:23,560 --> 00:05:25,040
Where else did he get the money

112
00:05:25,040 --> 00:05:26,560
to fool around in Tokyo?

113
00:05:28,510 --> 00:05:29,630
There sure are some impressive individuals

114
00:05:29,630 --> 00:05:31,630
hidden among us military students.

115
00:05:34,720 --> 00:05:35,560
Tufang.

116
00:05:35,920 --> 00:05:36,850
Look who's here.

117
00:05:39,920 --> 00:05:42,650
Young Prince Zaizheng came to meet you in person.

118
00:05:43,390 --> 00:05:45,790
I've heard a lot about you, Brother Tufang.

119
00:05:46,950 --> 00:05:47,810
Your Highness.

120
00:05:49,040 --> 00:05:50,600
Call me Zaizheng.

121
00:05:51,040 --> 00:05:53,700
We're family, there's no need for formalities.

122
00:05:54,180 --> 00:05:54,860
Renjun.

123
00:06:04,810 --> 00:06:06,570
Let's go.

124
00:06:08,550 --> 00:06:09,210
Have a seat.

125
00:06:16,720 --> 00:06:18,120
I came from Osaka.

126
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:23,510
[Son of Prince Qing, Yikuang, the Prime Minister of Foreign Affairs]
[Aisin Gioro Zaizheng]

127
00:06:18,460 --> 00:06:19,600
They are holding

128
00:06:19,630 --> 00:06:22,310
the National Industrial Exhibition over there.

129
00:06:22,310 --> 00:06:24,890
The night was lit by colorful lights, and the roads were wide and even.

130
00:06:24,890 --> 00:06:27,630
Western buildings with eight-sided window lattices were everywhere.

131
00:06:27,630 --> 00:06:28,750
The glass has five colors,

132
00:06:28,750 --> 00:06:31,010
and carriages and horses chase the wind.

133
00:06:35,310 --> 00:06:36,830
Father told me about you,

134
00:06:36,920 --> 00:06:38,270
someone from the imperial clan,

135
00:06:38,270 --> 00:06:39,120
studying

136
00:06:39,270 --> 00:06:40,800
military affairs in Japan.

137
00:06:41,390 --> 00:06:42,120
Prince Qing?

138
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:42,950
Yes.

139
00:06:43,830 --> 00:06:45,120
He found your name

140
00:06:45,120 --> 00:06:46,120
in the clan book

141
00:06:46,120 --> 00:06:47,320
of the Imperial Clan.

142
00:06:47,920 --> 00:06:49,159
Thatâ€™s why he sent an order

143
00:06:49,159 --> 00:06:52,159
to pick you out from the Banner Battalion in Jingzhou.

144
00:06:52,920 --> 00:06:53,870
I see.

145
00:06:54,720 --> 00:06:55,560
For this,

146
00:06:55,920 --> 00:06:58,159
he even reported to the Empress Dowager.

147
00:06:58,159 --> 00:06:59,830
Her Majesty showed great approval

148
00:06:59,830 --> 00:07:01,030
of this arrangement.

149
00:07:03,480 --> 00:07:05,310
I didn't know that was what happened.

150
00:07:05,310 --> 00:07:06,840
I neglected your kindness.

151
00:07:07,480 --> 00:07:09,160
My sincere apologies.

152
00:07:18,160 --> 00:07:20,600
Actually, your spot

153
00:07:20,600 --> 00:07:22,400
belonged to my younger brother.

154
00:07:26,240 --> 00:07:26,920
I know.

155
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:30,120
He's not as good as you.

156
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,659
He was very spoiled when he was young.

157
00:07:33,000 --> 00:07:34,530
If we had given him the spot,

158
00:07:34,600 --> 00:07:36,060
it would have been wasted.

159
00:07:36,180 --> 00:07:37,510
So Father didn't agree.

160
00:07:38,470 --> 00:07:39,800
He thinks highly of you.

161
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,130
When I came to Tokyo,

162
00:07:41,430 --> 00:07:42,830
he specifically asked me

163
00:07:42,980 --> 00:07:44,060
to meet you

164
00:07:44,430 --> 00:07:45,960
and evaluate you in person.

165
00:07:50,270 --> 00:07:52,000
He has chosen the right person.

166
00:07:52,159 --> 00:07:53,690
You hold a fiery gaze in your eyes,

167
00:07:53,690 --> 00:07:55,490
and you look like a man of skills.

168
00:07:56,600 --> 00:07:57,400
When I go back,

169
00:07:57,430 --> 00:07:59,000
I'll report to him.

170
00:07:59,120 --> 00:08:00,450
He will be happy to know.

171
00:08:10,240 --> 00:08:10,870
This is...

172
00:08:11,830 --> 00:08:12,360
Father asked me

173
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:13,830
to bring you this money.

174
00:08:14,720 --> 00:08:16,720
I can't accept it.

175
00:08:16,720 --> 00:08:17,650
Absolutely not.

176
00:08:18,760 --> 00:08:20,440
The court issued this money.

177
00:08:20,770 --> 00:08:21,900
Father approved it.

178
00:08:22,600 --> 00:08:24,040
He wants you to use it

179
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,480
to recruit military talent in Tokyo.

180
00:08:26,480 --> 00:08:28,230
He wants me to do it?

181
00:08:32,110 --> 00:08:33,270
The rebels in Tokyo

182
00:08:34,000 --> 00:08:35,929
are fighting for military talent.

183
00:08:35,960 --> 00:08:38,080
We can't win without money.

184
00:08:39,270 --> 00:08:40,440
Currently, the imperial court

185
00:08:40,440 --> 00:08:42,039
is reorganizing the military

186
00:08:42,039 --> 00:08:43,320
and establishing a new army.

187
00:08:43,320 --> 00:08:44,980
We lack reliable individuals

188
00:08:45,160 --> 00:08:46,360
who can lead the army.

189
00:08:47,010 --> 00:08:48,090
Use this money

190
00:08:48,200 --> 00:08:50,200
to pay for meals and solve problems.

191
00:08:50,230 --> 00:08:51,630
Gather some popularity.

192
00:08:52,360 --> 00:08:53,490
Gather popularity?

193
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:57,240
Brother Tufang.

194
00:08:57,510 --> 00:08:58,550
From now on,

195
00:08:59,000 --> 00:09:00,440
don't think of yourself

196
00:09:00,500 --> 00:09:01,530
as a soldier.

197
00:09:02,630 --> 00:09:03,990
Think of yourself as the future

198
00:09:03,990 --> 00:09:06,190
military leader of the imperial court.

199
00:09:17,360 --> 00:09:18,630
The imperial clan

200
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,600
needs a new military talent.

201
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:24,080
Father has placed his hopes in you.

202
00:09:36,520 --> 00:09:39,400
I'm here. Nice to meet you.

203
00:09:39,830 --> 00:09:40,760
You're here.

204
00:09:42,030 --> 00:09:42,840
Have you eaten?

205
00:09:42,840 --> 00:09:43,790
I've eaten.

206
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:49,030
What should I call you?

207
00:09:49,270 --> 00:09:50,530
My name is Xie Shuhong.

208
00:09:50,700 --> 00:09:51,490
Shuhong.

209
00:09:52,390 --> 00:09:54,590
Shu as in "grains", and Hong as in "red."

210
00:09:56,630 --> 00:09:57,390
Wait here.

211
00:10:00,960 --> 00:10:01,600
Here.

212
00:10:10,270 --> 00:10:13,480
It's red too.

213
00:10:14,630 --> 00:10:16,770
Yes, but it's much prettier than me.

214
00:10:17,160 --> 00:10:19,680
Cai Guangqi, too.

215
00:10:20,600 --> 00:10:22,340
This is also Mr. Cai's work?

216
00:10:23,100 --> 00:10:25,100
He's good.

217
00:10:25,720 --> 00:10:29,360
I like black and red.

218
00:10:29,910 --> 00:10:30,910
He uses them well.

219
00:10:34,070 --> 00:10:34,640
Here.

220
00:10:39,150 --> 00:10:39,840
You do it.

221
00:10:47,440 --> 00:10:50,040
23 in total.

222
00:10:49,690 --> 00:10:52,520
[A directory of Qing painters - Songyun Hall]

223
00:10:51,030 --> 00:10:52,600
They are all good.

224
00:10:54,600 --> 00:10:55,330
Understood.

225
00:10:55,600 --> 00:10:57,750
The shop sells art by these artists.

226
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,510
Keep it.

227
00:11:00,200 --> 00:11:01,000
For me?

228
00:11:01,600 --> 00:11:02,400
There's more.

229
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,270
This is a map.

230
00:11:07,760 --> 00:11:09,720
[Tokyo City Map]

231
00:11:08,630 --> 00:11:09,790
Is it for me too?

232
00:11:10,910 --> 00:11:11,710
There's more.

233
00:11:15,030 --> 00:11:15,600
This.

234
00:11:16,280 --> 00:11:17,070
And...

235
00:11:19,710 --> 00:11:20,400
This.

236
00:11:22,030 --> 00:11:24,550
These are all for you.

237
00:11:26,360 --> 00:11:29,910
Your work for today.

238
00:11:33,150 --> 00:11:35,030
Five orders in total.

239
00:11:35,320 --> 00:11:39,130
All the requirements are written down.

240
00:11:39,270 --> 00:11:40,000
Understood?

241
00:11:40,650 --> 00:11:41,380
Understood.

242
00:11:41,390 --> 00:11:43,720
It's the content and size of the art piece.

243
00:11:43,910 --> 00:11:45,240
I'll be counting on you.

244
00:11:56,630 --> 00:11:57,510
Excuse me.

245
00:12:00,480 --> 00:12:01,790
Where is this?

246
00:12:01,910 --> 00:12:04,000
This place? That way.

247
00:12:08,200 --> 00:12:09,650
Tianxiang's suggestion is good.

248
00:12:09,650 --> 00:12:10,240
Come on,

249
00:12:10,240 --> 00:12:11,480
let's continue after a drink.

250
00:12:11,480 --> 00:12:12,360
That makes sense.

251
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:13,910
Shuhong, add some tea.

252
00:12:17,480 --> 00:12:18,480
Wait, Tianxiang.

253
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:20,210
I have to make tea myself today.

254
00:12:21,800 --> 00:12:22,560
Look at you.

255
00:12:22,580 --> 00:12:24,160
I was just about to gather my thoughts.

256
00:12:24,160 --> 00:12:25,480
What can he do?

257
00:12:25,580 --> 00:12:27,980
Shuhong had washed her hands of the matter.

258
00:12:28,030 --> 00:12:28,960
Where did she go?

259
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:32,030
She went to the ink painting place.

260
00:12:32,430 --> 00:12:33,640
Ink painting?

261
00:12:33,750 --> 00:12:35,550
She's working for painters now.

262
00:12:36,120 --> 00:12:36,790
Painter?

263
00:12:37,360 --> 00:12:38,560
What kind of painter?

264
00:12:38,940 --> 00:12:40,470
Painters like Cai Guangqi.

265
00:12:41,370 --> 00:12:42,770
There are dozens of them.

266
00:12:42,890 --> 00:12:43,680
Dozens?

267
00:12:52,120 --> 00:12:52,910
Coming.

268
00:12:58,500 --> 00:12:59,830
Are you Mr. Zhu Wentong?

269
00:13:00,790 --> 00:13:01,550
Yes.

270
00:13:02,280 --> 00:13:04,610
I'm from Mr. Kanyama's stationery store.

271
00:13:05,910 --> 00:13:06,670
Come in.

272
00:13:14,160 --> 00:13:15,690
I've never seen you before.

273
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:17,930
Are you new here?

274
00:13:18,150 --> 00:13:18,910
Yes.

275
00:13:20,390 --> 00:13:22,120
Mr. Kanyama would like to congratulate you.

276
00:13:22,120 --> 00:13:23,000
Another order for

277
00:13:23,000 --> 00:13:25,330
a four-foot painting of a crane has arrived.

278
00:13:25,330 --> 00:13:27,190
What's there to congratulate me?

279
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:30,200
I've already talked to him.

280
00:13:30,910 --> 00:13:32,000
I won't make

281
00:13:33,110 --> 00:13:33,960
any more

282
00:13:34,960 --> 00:13:36,440
traditional realistic crane paintings.

283
00:13:36,440 --> 00:13:37,030
But...

284
00:13:37,940 --> 00:13:39,940
Isn't this a forced purchase?

285
00:13:41,120 --> 00:13:42,760
I'm not short of money.

286
00:13:56,270 --> 00:13:58,120
This is a whole sheet of Shuxuan paper.

287
00:13:58,120 --> 00:13:59,850
I can tell by a single touch that

288
00:13:59,910 --> 00:14:01,000
this is an authentic product

289
00:14:01,000 --> 00:14:02,030
from Xuancheng County.

290
00:14:02,030 --> 00:14:04,150
How can Japan make this?

