Good.

879
00:39:40,320 --> 00:39:41,360
Just one.

880
00:39:42,070 --> 00:39:43,730
We can print as many as we want.

881
00:39:43,800 --> 00:39:45,330
By that time, we'll become a bank. Right?

882
00:39:45,330 --> 00:39:46,190
It can save a lot of trouble.

883
00:39:46,190 --> 00:39:47,030
Just draw one,

884
00:39:47,130 --> 00:39:49,090
and we don't need to worry about money for the rest of our lives.

885
00:39:49,090 --> 00:39:50,370
You little girl.

886
00:39:51,030 --> 00:39:52,630
You're really imaginative.

887
00:39:52,880 --> 00:39:54,280
Is there such a good thing?

888
00:39:54,280 --> 00:39:55,840
Just draw according to the rules.

889
00:39:55,840 --> 00:39:57,880
Someone else will take care of the rest.

890
00:39:57,880 --> 00:39:58,580
Other painters

891
00:39:58,580 --> 00:39:59,310
are not as

892
00:39:59,340 --> 00:40:00,860
meticulous as you, right?

893
00:40:03,070 --> 00:40:05,480
Who are you talking about?

894
00:40:06,840 --> 00:40:09,320
Have you heard of the Revolutionary Party?

895
00:40:12,560 --> 00:40:13,520
Party members?

896
00:40:14,900 --> 00:40:15,630
Revolution?

897
00:40:15,910 --> 00:40:16,710
That's right.

898
00:40:17,100 --> 00:40:18,830
They asked me to ask you

899
00:40:19,630 --> 00:40:21,280
to draw just one banknote

900
00:40:21,920 --> 00:40:22,920
of 10 yuan

901
00:40:22,920 --> 00:40:24,380
of Imperial Bank of China.

902
00:40:24,800 --> 00:40:25,400
Okay?

903
00:40:28,070 --> 00:40:28,920
Little girl,

904
00:40:30,110 --> 00:40:31,760
how old are you?

905
00:40:33,510 --> 00:40:35,630
My nominal age is 19.

906
00:40:35,920 --> 00:40:37,320
You are young

907
00:40:38,220 --> 00:40:40,460
and pretty.

908
00:40:42,760 --> 00:40:43,800
What a pity.

909
00:40:45,790 --> 00:40:48,780
It's really a pity.

910
00:40:50,950 --> 00:40:52,840
Take this.

911
00:40:54,960 --> 00:40:57,860
Consider it my donation to your revolution.

912
00:40:58,550 --> 00:40:59,070
This...

913
00:40:59,770 --> 00:41:02,120
Take this two-crane painting too.

914
00:41:03,920 --> 00:41:04,760
But...

915
00:41:05,320 --> 00:41:07,070
tell Mr. Kanyama,

916
00:41:08,070 --> 00:41:08,840
from now on,

917
00:41:09,840 --> 00:41:11,710
I won't sell

918
00:41:12,880 --> 00:41:14,600
any crane painting again.

919
00:41:15,680 --> 00:41:16,240
Take it.

920
00:41:17,240 --> 00:41:18,970
You haven't stamped your seal.

921
00:41:20,910 --> 00:41:22,020
Let me help you.

922
00:41:23,830 --> 00:41:25,490
What? He doesn't want to draw?

923
00:41:27,390 --> 00:41:29,070
How can you be so straightforward?

924
00:41:29,070 --> 00:41:30,150
You'll scare

925
00:41:30,150 --> 00:41:31,080
old Mr. Zhu away.

926
00:41:31,190 --> 00:41:32,430
When it comes to such a scary deal,

927
00:41:32,430 --> 00:41:33,400
you will scare even the donkey away

928
00:41:33,400 --> 00:41:34,860
when you tell him about it.

929
00:41:36,510 --> 00:41:37,590
You should have reasoned with him

930
00:41:37,590 --> 00:41:39,320
and treated him with kindness.

931
00:41:39,480 --> 00:41:40,840
How should I reason with him?

932
00:41:40,840 --> 00:41:42,240
Not to mention kindness.

933
00:41:43,190 --> 00:41:44,680
You should have argued the case for revolution

934
00:41:44,680 --> 00:41:46,610
and expressed the grief of people.

935
00:41:52,230 --> 00:41:53,360
Where is my digest?

936
00:41:53,920 --> 00:41:54,840
What digest?

937
00:41:55,550 --> 00:41:57,410
It's Brother Zou Rong's new work.

938
00:41:59,280 --> 00:41:59,990
Yes.

939
00:42:00,280 --> 00:42:01,030
It's here.

940
00:42:01,510 --> 00:42:03,170
Let me read a paragraph to you.

941
00:42:03,590 --> 00:42:05,590
Listen to this. Just one paragraph.

942
00:42:06,710 --> 00:42:07,800
To sweep away

943
00:42:08,070 --> 00:42:11,710
thousands of years of authoritarianism.

944
00:42:12,220 --> 00:42:13,050
To shed away

945
00:42:13,550 --> 00:42:17,000
thousands of years of slavery.

946
00:42:18,030 --> 00:42:19,110
To wash away

947
00:42:19,840 --> 00:42:21,550
the shame of

948
00:42:21,580 --> 00:42:25,410
260 years of cruelty and abuse,

949
00:42:30,590 --> 00:42:33,840
and make mainland China a clean land.

950
00:42:35,590 --> 00:42:39,050
The Emperor's descendants continue to live on prosperously.

951
00:42:40,360 --> 00:42:42,150
Some resurrected,

952
00:42:42,150 --> 00:42:43,360
and returned to their senses.

953
00:42:43,360 --> 00:42:44,590
They got out of the 18 layers of hell,

954
00:42:44,590 --> 00:42:46,150
ascended to the 33 levels of heaven,

955
00:42:46,150 --> 00:42:48,280
and are full of zeal and vigor.

956
00:42:48,280 --> 00:42:50,360
They think they are the best and most unique.

957
00:42:50,360 --> 00:42:52,760
A purpose of greatness and excellence

958
00:42:53,280 --> 00:42:53,800
lies in

959
00:42:54,510 --> 00:42:55,440
the revolution.
